name: Night Reflection Twelve by Kim Henry & Eric Pare

metadata.name: Night Reflection 12.1
metadata.description: Urban escape is a chapter dedicated to our rare artistic explorations in cities. Urban areas represent an abundance of energy, movement and lights that we capture from our personal perspective. Thousands of city lights unifying to create an entity that becomes our luminous background. Its glow and energy is merging with our ephemeral traces of light.
